t working with the mozilla/TTS repository, although, the result is not great yet (I am using a custom dataset) and sometimes the training crashes with `RuntimeError:  [!] NaN loss with decoder_loss.`, especially if I use `\"signal_norm\": true`.\r\n\r\nDo you have any suggestions for implementing this together with the Nvidia/Tacotron2? Are there any key differences that you can point out, which should be considered?\r\n\r\nThe Mozilla's OriginalAttention implementation works well together with the Nvidia's Tacotron 2 implementation. Is it possible to interchange the attention without changing the rest of the model/hparams?","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mozilla/TTS/issues/comments/791363814/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"nicemanis","id":9463816,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjk0NjM4MTY=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/9463816?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis","html_url":"https://github.com/nicemanis","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mozilla/TTS/issues/comments/792793389","html_url":"https://github.com/mozilla/TTS/issues/675#issuecomment-792793389","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mozilla/TTS/issues/675","id":792793389,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDc5Mjc5MzM4OQ==","user":{"login":"nicemanis","id":9463816,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjk0NjM4MTY=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/9463816?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis","html_url":"https://github.com/nicemanis","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2021-03-08T14:31:06Z","updated_at":"2021-03-09T08:00:46Z","author_association":"NONE","body":"I compared the OriginalAttention implementations and noticed some differences in the masking and normalization:\r\n\r\nMozilla/TTS\r\n```\r\n# apply masking\r\nif mask is not None:\r\n  attention.data.masked_fill_(~mask, self._mask_value)\r\n\r\n...\r\n\r\n# normalize attention values\r\nif self.norm == \"softmax\":\r\n  alignment = torch.softmax(attention, dim=-1)\r\n```\r\n\r\nNvidia/Tacotron2\r\n```\r\nif mask is not None:\r\n  alignment.data.masked_fill_(mask, self.score_mask_value)\r\n\r\nattention_weights = F.softmax(alignment, dim=1)\r\n```\r\n\r\nIf I use the Mozilla's attention implementation together with the Nvidia's Tacotron 2, it produces `nan` values. Why is the mask inverted in the Mozilla's case?\r\n\r\nEDIT: I noticed that Nvidia's implementation already applies the tilde op when computing the mask:\r\n```\r\nself.initialize_decoder_states(memory, mask=~get_mask_from_lengths(memory_lengths))\r\n```","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mozilla/TTS/issues/comments/792793389/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"nicemanis","id":9463816,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjk0NjM4MTY=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/9463816?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis","html_url":"https://github.com/nicemanis","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/nicemanis/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mozilla/TTS/issues/comments/853161745","html_url":"https://github.com/mozilla/TTS/issues/675#issuecomment-853161745","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mozilla/TTS/issues/675","id":853161745,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDg1MzE2MTc0NQ==","user":{"login":"stale[bot]","id":26384082,"node_id":"MDM6Qm90MjYzODQwODI=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/in/1724?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/stale%5Bbot%5D","html_url":"https://github.com/apps/stale","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/stale%5Bbot%5D/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/stale%5Bbot%5D/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/stale%5Bbot%5D/gists{/gist_id}","starred